reviewText:
I'm a professional jazz musician....guitar, alto sax....so I know what I'm talking about.

This is the best video I have.
(1)Charlie Parker/Dizzy Gillespie "Hot House"
(2)Thelonius Monk "Epistrophy" with Charlie Rouse on tenor
(3)Bud Powell & Charles Mingus "I'll Remember April"
(4)Bud Powell Trio "Shaw'Nuff" with Kenny Clark on Drums
(5)Art Blakey & the Jazz Messengers "Blues March" Paris...Lee Morgan,Wayne Shorter
(6)Kenny Clarke Quintet "Just a Blues Riff"
(7)Jay Jay Johnson All-Stars  "Buzzy"; "Lover Man" & "Now's The Time"

Get it while you can.
